data.description: Welcome to your income producing opportunity! This fully remodeled 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem is not just a residence—it's an investment. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this property combines modern elegance with income-generating potential. Fully renovated main floor with another fully renovated studio apartment/mother-in-law suite. It does have separate entrance and separate meter. New Roof (2023), New windows (2023), newly remodeled kitchens both upstairs and downstairs. New flooring and paint throughout. Large lot with beautiful mature trees. This home is in an established neighborhood, with close proximity to Downtown, Governor's Square Mall, and Ft Campbell Military Base. Seller offering $5000 in concessions.
